.IP "\fBraster\fR=\fIname\fR" 4m
.br
Raster map from which to copy color table
.IP "\fBraster_3d\fR=\fIname\fR" 4m
.br
3D raster map from which to copy color table
.IP "\fBrules\fR=\fIname\fR" 4m
.br
Path to rules file
.br
\(dq\-\(dq to read rules from stdin
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fIr3.colors\fR has exactly the same functionality
as \fIr.colors\fR but for 3D raster maps. Please refer
to \fIr.colors\fR.
.SH EXAMPLES
.br
.nf
\fC
r3.colors map=volume_1 color=gyr
\fR
.fi
